&lt;p&gt;Prior to the commencement of the development, full details of the&amp;nbsp; outdoor unit for cooling and enclosure shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority, including noise impact assessment.&amp;nbsp; The noise level from all plant and machinery included in the approved development shall at all times remain 5dB(A) below background levels when measured at any nearby residential window.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: To ensure that occupiers of neighbouring premises do not suffer a loss of amenity by reason of noise nuisance and other excess noise.
&lt;/p&gt;
